      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like a pattern that's impossible to break. like, no matter how much i talk or how many people try to help, the outcome is always the same. it's just a loop of trying and failing and feeling like shit. it feels like there's no real way out of it other than just... stopping. stop trying, stop the whole thing. it's just so heavy.",
